%%
% ChatGPT used for 'video plots' of the solutions Below:
%% ================================================================
% ANIMATION of KKT receding-horizon execution
%   subplot 1 → (theta,theta_dot) vs k (closed-loop + predicted)
%   subplot 2 → (theta,theta_dot) closed-loop + predicted
